    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简介</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《猫咪乌托邦》是一款基于动量的2D平台游戏，玩家将使用钓鱼线抓钩摆荡，穿梭于不同的路径，帮助猫咪的朋友们解锁不同的结局，并使用强大的游戏内编辑器创建自定义关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305690/extras/afb0e0eae68dcb2352c40b81fb93bbac.poster.avif?t=1772390825\" width=960 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305690/extras/afb0e0eae68dcb2352c40b81fb93bbac.webm?t=1772390825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >功能</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>街机模式：</strong> 通过具有挑战性但可重复游玩的挑战来解锁关卡和结局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>练习模式：</strong> 优化关卡通关时间并观看已保存的最佳记录回放</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>日志模式：</strong> 跨多个平台跟踪详细的关卡进度、记录和统计数据类别</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>钓鱼：</strong> 寻找并捕捉隐藏在各个关卡中的各种鱼类</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>迷你游戏：</strong> 完成额外的关卡，体验独特的挑战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>艺术画廊：</strong> 解锁后，自由欣赏插图并聆听音乐</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关卡编辑器：</strong> 创建您自己的相互关联的自定义关卡集</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自定义：</strong> 通过更改鱼线和鱼饵的颜色来个性化您的 Catto</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam 排行榜：</strong> 与社区竞争，提升您的排行榜排名</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam 创意工坊：</strong> 分享您自己的自定义关卡，并畅玩社区制作的其他关卡</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305690/extras/85d4b1e449c6b0f3063ff9c914baf5f2.webp?t=1772390825\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305690/extras/85d4b1e449c6b0f3063ff9c914baf5f2.poster.avif?t=1772390825\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1010 height=305 /></picture></span></p>",
